tool_input.description: Get summary of changed files vs main

tool_input.command:
gh pr create --title "feat: #4 - New agent" --body "$(cat <<'EOF'
## Summary

- Adds a new `documenter` agent as the final step in the team workflow
- The documenter generates documentation for completed features after all builders finish and validators confirm everything works
- Updates `team-lead` agent to invoke the documenter as the last step in the pipeline

## Implementation Plan

See: [specs/issue-4-adw-1d7283ec-sdlc_planner-add-documenter-agent.md](specs/issue-4-adw-1d7283ec-sdlc_planner-add-documenter-agent.md)

## Key Changes

- `.kiro/agents/documenter.json` — new documenter agent configuration
- `.kiro/agents/documenter-prompt.md` — documenter agent prompt defining its role and behavior
- `.kiro/agents/team-lead-prompt.md` — updated to include documenter as final workflow step
- `.kiro/agents/team-lead.json` — updated agent list to include documenter
- `README.md` — updated workflow documentation to reflect new agent
- `.claude/commands/e2e/test_documenter_agent.md` — E2E test for the documenter agent

## Checklist

- [x] Documenter agent created with prompt and config
- [x] Team lead updated to invoke documenter as final step
- [x] E2E test added for documenter agent
- [x] README updated with new workflow diagram

Closes #4

ADW tracking ID: 1d7283ec
EOF
)" --base main 2>&1
